                  'Servidor compatible con MCP (transporte stdio)',
                  'Herramientas switch_model / list_models / get_status / exit_switcher',
                  'Impulsado por protocolo: toda la configuraciĂłn desde manifiestos ai-protocol',
                  'Multi-proveedor: OpenAI, Anthropic, Google, DeepSeek, etc.',
                  'Python + ai-lib-python SDK, configuraciĂłn automĂˇtica del protocolo',
                ]}
                link="https://github.com/ailib-official/spiderswitch"
                github="https://github.com/ailib-official/spiderswitch"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Core Philosophy -->
      <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="text-center mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[var(--text)] mb-4">
              DiseĂ±o impulsado por protocolo
            </h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-[var(--text-dim)] max-w-2xl mx-auto">
              Â«Toda la lĂłgica son operadores, toda la configuraciĂłn es protocolo.Â» Todo el
              comportamiento del proveedor se declara en YAML â€?los runtimes contienen cero lĂłgica
              hardcodeada de proveedores.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--bg-card)]">
              <div
                class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-purple-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4"
              >
                <svg
                  class="w-5 h-5 text-purple-400"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  stroke-width="2"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"
                  ></path>
